   rev:'Recovery, improving finances, overcoming hardship, asking for help, spiritual renewal, finding support',
   meaning:'The Five of Pentacles shows two figures in the cold — heads down, ragged, struggling through the snow — passing directly beneath a warmly lit stained glass window. The light is right there. The warmth is right there. And they\'re so consumed by the weight of what they\'re going through that they haven\'t looked up to see it. This card carries real compassion for genuine hardship.',
