   rev:'Laziness, stagnation, boredom, stuck in routine, uncreative, obsessive, all work no progress',
   meaning:'The Knight of Pentacles sits on a heavy, dark horse that is completely still — not rearing, not galloping, not even walking. Just planted. This is the most grounded and least glamorous of the Knights, and he knows it — and he doesn\'t care. While the other knights are off charging into battles, the Knight of Pentacles is tilling the field, preparing for the harvest, thinking about the long-term future. His results are built to last.',
